methods.authenticate:
Authenticate and obtain an AuthContext using the provided protocol and byte payload.

:param protocolVersion: (long) - the protocol version to use (application specific)
:param payload: (com.google.protobuf.ByteString) - the user's login details (protocol specific)
:return: (io.deephaven.util.auth.AuthContext) null if user could not be authenticated, otherwise an AuthContext for the user
methods.supportsProtocol:
Returns true if this auth context provider can authenticate using the provided protocol version.

:param authProtocol: (long) - the protocol version to use (application specific)
:return: (boolean) true iff `authProtocol` is supported
